## Version 8.4.1

- basic feature export framework
- configuration now accepts multiple comma-separated paths
- improved config error reporting 

## Version 8.4.0

- added functions to scale GDAL rasters
- fixed CRS transformation issues for certain projections
- fixed concurrency issues with temporary files
